sequenceDiagram
participant DOM as index.html
participant App as NodgesApp
participant Three as THREE.Scene Renderer Camera
participant Managers as Core Utils
participant Data as data examples *.json
participant Worker as layout-worker

DOM->>App: Initialize NodgesApp
App->>Three: initThreeJS()
App->>Managers: initManagers() (State, Event, Layout, UI, ...)
App->>Managers: initGUI(), initEventListeners()
App->>Data: loadDefaultData("data/examples/small.json")
Data-->>App: JSON (legacy | future)
App->>Managers: if future -> FutureDataParser/Validator
App->>App: currentNodes/currentEdges setzen
App->>App: createNodes(), createEdges()
opt LayoutEnabled
App->>LM: applyLayout("force-directed", nodes, edges)
LM->>Worker: compute positions (iterations)
Worker-->>LM: positions updates
LM-->>App: updateNodePositions()
end
loop RAF
App->>Three: renderer.render(scene, camera)
App->>S: state.animate() (z.B. Glow)
end
